              "id": "ef3ae158",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<h2>Midland Floor Care FAQs:</h2>\n01. What types of commercial flooring do you specialize in cleaning?\n\n<b>Carpet, Natural Stone, VCT, LVT, Tile &amp; Grout and various other flooring types</b>\n\n\n02. How often should I schedule professional floor care for my business?\n\n<b>Recommended frequency of service depends on the amount of foot traffic in your facility</b>\n\n\n03. Can you provide a customized floor care plan based on our specific needs?\n\n<b>Of course! Schedule a site visit <a href=\"/schedule-a-visit/\">here</a>.</b>\n\n\n04. Do you offer eco-friendly or green cleaning options for commercial floors?\n\n<b>Yes, we proudly offer eco-friendly and green cleaning options for commercial floors.</b>\n\n\n05. What is the estimated cost for your commercial floor care services?\n\n<b>Our rates are quoted per square foot and based on what it would take to give our clients their desired result.</b>\n\n\n06. How long does it typically take to clean and maintain commercial flooring?\n\n<b>Depending on the flooring type, amount of square footage and the cleaning method employed, cleaning times vary per project.</b>\n\n\n07. Do you provide emergency or after-hours floor care services?\n<b>Certainly, we do offer emergency and after-hours floor care services to accommodate your needs.</b>\n\n\n08. What measures do you take to ensure the safety of our employees and customers during cleaning?\n\n<b>In addition to using eco-friendly cleaning chemistry we also recommend scheduling service after hours when the majority of your staff has already left for the work day.</b>\n\n\n09. Is your team trained and certified in commercial floor care services?\n\n<b>Yes, our team undergoes ongoing training and certifications</b>\n\n<img src=\"http://midlandfloors.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/IMG_1830-1.jpg\" alt=\"image\" />\n<h2>Service Area:</h2>\nWe Proudly serving Washington, DC, Prince George\u2019s County MD, Charles County MD, Anne Arundel MD, Montgomery County MD, Fairfax County VA, and beyond\n<h5>Needs Any Help?</h5>\nFeel Free to Call us\u00a0 get your next Floor Care Audit.\n\n<!-- Style 1 Start -->\n<img src=\"https://tv.fixherotheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/con-i2.png\" alt=\"Contact Title\" />\nCall 9-5pm Week Days\n<a href=\"tel:(240)532-9097\">(240) 532-9097</a>\n<!-- Style 1 End -->\n\n<a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/7-essential-tips-for-impeccable-commercial-floor-care-services/\">7 Essential Tips for Impeccable Commercial Floor Care Services</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/\">Home</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/floor-care-services/\">Services</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/about/\">About Midland</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/eco-friendly-floor-solutions-for-retail-stores/\">Eco-Friendly Floor Solutions for Retail Stores</a><div style=\"background:#F3FCF4;border-left:4px solid #43A94B;padding:18px 22px;margin-top:24px;border-radius:6px\"><p style=\"margin:0 0 10px;font-size:13px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#0F1411\">Related Services</p><ul style=\"margin:0;padding-left:18px;line-height:1.9\"><li><a href=\"/long-term-recurring-commercial-floor-care-programs/\" style=\"color:#2F8137;font-weight:700\">Long-Term & Recurring Commercial Floor Care Services</a></li><li><a href=\"/customized-commercial-floor-care-solutions/\" style=\"color:#2F8137;font-weight:700\">Customized Commercial Floor Care Solutions</a></li><li><a href=\"/janitorial-housekeeping-facility-services/\" style=\"color:#2F8137;font-weight:700\">Janitorial & Housekeeping Facility Services</a></li><li><a href=\"/commercial-upholstery/\" style=\"color:#2F8137;font-weight:700\">Commercial Upholstery</a></li><li><a href=\"/commercial-tile-grout-cleaning-services/\" style=\"color:#2F8137;font-weight:700\">Commercial Tile & Grout Cleaning</a></li><li><a href=\"/commercial-carpet-cleaning-services/\" style=\"color:#2F8137;font-weight:700\">Commercial Carpet Cleaning Services</a></li></ul></div>",
                "align": "left",
                "text_color": "#0F1411",
                "typography_typography": "custom",
